quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  51,7,"Mi woo…óndirii kammu jom …óate nguun !"
  51,8,"Pellet, ho…óon e konngol luurrangol."
  51,9,"Hino yiltee e makko kala firlitaa…óo e gooŇč…óinal."
  51,10,"Fenoo…ďe …ďeen ku…óaama."
  51,11,"…ďeen yollii…ďe e majjere welsindii…ďe."
  51,12,"He…ďe la…ďndoo : "Ko honnde woni √Ďalaande njo…ďdi kuu…óe?""
  51,13,"√Ďalaande nde …ďe leptoytee…ďe ta Yiite :"
  51,14,""Mee…óee lepte mon …óeen; ko …óum woni ko keppatno…óon ko"."
  51,15,"Pellet, gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen wonii e aljannaaji e …ďulli."
  51,16,"Jaggitoo…ďe ko Joom ma…ď…ďe okki…ďe …ďe ko adii …óuum ko…ďe mo∆ī∆īinatnoo…ďe."
  51,17,"He…ďe pam…óuno ko…ďe …óaanatoo jehma."
  51,18,"E saanga ndoogu he…ďe toro yaafeede."
  51,19,"Ina e jaw…óe mu'en hakke wonan'de √Īaagatoo…ďe e …ďe √Īaagataako."
  51,20,"Ina e ndeer leydi he Ma'andeeji wonan'de yananaa…ďe."
  51,21,"E ndeer pittaali mon mate on teskataaka."
  51,22,"Ina e kammu arsuka mon e ko podante …óon ko."
  51,23,"E Joom kammu e leydi ko …óum goongo hono no kaalirton nih."
  51,24,"Mbele arii e maa yeewtere ho…ó…ďe Ibraahiima teddinaa…ďe …ďe."
  51,25,"Tuma …ďe naatnoo ka makko …ďe mbi'i: "Salaam (Kisal mon)". O maaki: "Minen ko men …óen∆īii …ďe on"."
  51,26,"O naayii fa'ade e koreeji makko o addori ngaari payndi."
  51,27,"O …ďadani…ďe ndi o wii on √Īaamata?"
  51,28,"O so*i e mu,'en kulol, …ďe mii woto hul, …ďe mbeltiniri…ďe cuklel."
  51,29,"Jom suudu makko ari hombo wulla o hellii ye'esa makko, o wii nayeejo dimara.?."
  51,30,"Maleykaaji …ói mbii ko hono nih Joom ma daali ko KaŇčko woni √Īee√Īo Ganndo."